    <td id="main">
      <div class="main">
      	      <div class="content">
        <div class="tabs"></div>
                  <div class="node">
    <div class="content"><table background="/images/home_bg.jpg" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td colspan="2">
<div style="padding: 20px;" align="justify">The National Centre for Biological Sciences (NCBS), located in  Bangalore, is part of the<a href="http://www.tifr.res.in/" target="_blank"> Tata Institute of Fundamental Research</a>.  The mandate of NCBS is fundamental research in the frontier areas of  biology. Our research interests range from the study of single molecules  to ecology and evolution. In addition we engage in a number of  collaborative initiatives, such as <a href="http://instem.res.in/" title="inStem">inStem</a> and the <a href="/node/369">iBio</a>;  and we help to develop cutting edge instrumentation and software via <a href="/ccamp" title="C-CAMP">C-CAMP</a>.</div>
</td>
</tr>
